{
  "manifest_version": "1.0",
  "_comment": "Sync-policy metadata for the Smart Sync registry. This file is hand-maintained; templates/manifest.json is auto-generated from it by tools/generate-manifest.py and must NOT be edited by hand (issue #207). `version` is read from each template's frontmatter when present; overrides here win. target_type defaults to HTOM for templates/htom/*, Spoke for templates/spoke/*, and both for root templates. `sync_rules` documents directory-level sync policy (issue #211); per-file behaviour is still driven by `overrides`.",
